VKontakte-Standalone version 0.1
=====================================

This module is a wrapper for easy calling of Vkontakte API methods.
It is able to automatically log in the user and allow any required
permissions.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

URI (core)
Carp (core)
WWW::Mechanize
JSON 

